summary: This document is a communication from an Assistant United States Attorney in the Southern District of New York, requesting service of a subpoena to Expedia for records relating to travel by Ghislaine Maxwell. It indicates an active investigation into Maxwell's movements.

events.title: Subpoena Issued to Expedia
events.description: An Assistant United States Attorney requests service of a subpoena to Expedia for records relating to Ghislaine Maxwell's travel.

locations: 1 St. Andrew's Plaza, New York, NY 10007
keyFacts: A subpoena was issued to Expedia on January 24, 2020, seeking travel records for Ghislaine Maxwell.
The request was made by an Assistant United States Attorney in the Southern District of New York.
This indicates an active investigative step to trace Maxwell's movements as part of the broader case.
